NIYAT KI MAINAY ISS WAQT KI NAMAZ, NAMAZAY _____________KI ALLAH JALLAJALALOHU KAY WASTAY MONH MAIRA KHANA-E-KA’BAH KI TARAF ALLAH-O-AKBAR!

SANNA
QIYAM; SUBHAANAKALLAAHUMMA WA BAYHAMDIKA WA TABARAKASMUKA WA TA’ALAA JADDUKA WA LA’AA ILAAHA GHAIRUK:
IF WITH THE CLASS AFTER THE IMAM STARTS THE NAMAZ THEN KEEP SILENT RECITING THE SANNA AND LISTEN THE RECITATION OF IMAM AND IF BE ALONE THEN AFTER THE SANNA RECITE TAUZ, TASMIYAH, SURA-E-FATIHA AND ANYONE CHAPTER OF HOLLY BOOK OF QUR’AN.
TAUZ
AAUZUBILLAAHAY MINASHSHETAANIR-RAJEEM;
TASMIYAH
BISMILLAAHIR-RAHMAANIR-RAHEEM;
SURA-E-FATIHA
ALHAMDULILLAAHAY RABBILAALAMEEN; AR-RAHMAANIR-RAHEEM; MAALIKAY YAUMIDDEEN; EYYAKA NABUDU WA EYYAKA NASTAEEN; EHDAYNASSIRATALMUSTAQEEM; SIRATALLAZEENA ANAMTA ALAIHIM; GHAIRILMAGHZUBAY ALAIHIM WA LAZZA’AAALLEEN:
AAMEEN:
SURA IKHLAS
QULHUWALLAAHU AHAD; ALLAAHUSSAMAD; LAMYALID; WA LAM YOULAD; WA LAM YA KULLAHOO KUFUWAN AHAD:
THEN SAYING ALLAAHOAKBAR GOES INTO THE RUKKU AND CATCH THE KNEES WITH THE FINGERS OF HANDS FIRMLY AND SO MUCH BOW DOWN THAT BACK BE EQUAL AND RECITE AT LEAST THREE TIMES;
TASBIHAY RAKKU
SUBHANA RABBIYALAZEEM:
IF THERE IS CLASS THEN ONLY IMAM SHOULD SAY TASMIE:
TASMIE
SAMIALLAAHULAYMANHAMIDAH
QAUMAH
THEN BOTH HANDS LIVE AWAY AND KEEP STAND STRAIGHT AND MUQTADI SAY TAHMEED:
TAHMEED
RABBANA LAKALHAMD
LONELY PRAYER OFFERING SAY TASMIH AND TAHMEED BOTH AND THEN SAYING ALLAAHOAKBAR GO INTO SAJDA. LIKEWISE THAT FIRST KNEES THEN HANDS UPON THE EARTH THEN NOSE AND THEN FOREHEAD HEARTILY TOUCH THE EARTH AND FACE BE KEPT BETWEEN BOTH HANDS AND MAN TO ARMS FROM RIBS AND FROM THIGHS KEEP AWAY AND TO THIGHS KEEP AWAY FROM SPINDLES AND ELBOWS SHOULD BE UP FROM THE EARTH AND OF BOTH FEET’S FINGERS BELLIES TOWARDS QIBLAH UPON THE EARTH BE WELL TOUCHED AND BE RECITED AT LEAST THREE TIMES;
SAJDA KI TASBIH
SUBHAANA RABBIYALALAA
JALSAH
THEN SAYING ALLAAHOAKBAR SIT ALIKE THAT FIRST OF ALL LIFT HIS FOREHEAD THEN NOSE THEN HANDS AND LAYING LEFT FOOT SIT UPON IT AND RIGHT FOOT KEEP STAND AND OF ITS FINGERS LIVE TOWARDS KHANA-E-KA’BA AND HANDS KEEP UPON THIGHS NEAR KNEES THAT FINGERS ALSO ARE TOWARDS THE KHANA-E-KA’BA. AND THEN SAYING ALLAAHOAKBAR TO INTO;
DOOSRA SAJDAH
LIKEWISE DO SECOND SAJDAH AND THEN SAYING ALLAAHOAKBAR BE STAND.
QIYAM
TASMIYAH, FATIHA AND ANY OTHER CHAPTER SHOULD BE RECITED AND RUKKU AND SAJOOD LIKEWISE BUT AFTER THE IMAM MUQTADI BISMILLAAH, FATIHA AND OTHER CHAPTER WILL NOT BE RECITED. HE WILL BE LIVE STAND SILENTLY.
QADAH
TASHHUD
ATTAHIYYATU LILLAAHAY WASSALAWAATU WATTAYYIBATU; ASSALAMU ALAIKA AYYUHANNABBIYYU WA RAHMATULLAAHAY WA BARAKATU; ASSALAMU ALAINA WA ALAA EBADILLAAHISSAALAYHEEN; ASHHADU ALLA’AA ILAAHA ILLALAAHU WA ASHHADU ANNA MUHAMMADAN ABDUHU WA RASULUH:
DAROOD SHARIF
ALLAAHUMMA SALLAY ALA MUHAMMADINV-VA ALAA AALAY MUHAMMADIN KAMA SALLAITA ALAA IBRAAHEEMA WA ALAA AALAY IBRAAHEEMA INNAKA HAMEEDUM-MAJEED; ALLAAHUMMA BARIK ALAA MUHAMMADINV-VA ALAA AALAY MUHAMMADIN KAMA BARAKTA ALAA IBRAAHEEMA WA ALAA AALAY IBRAAHEEMA INNAKA HAMEEDUM-MAJEED:
RIBBIJALNI MUQEEMASSALAATI WA MIN ZURRIYYATI; RABBANA WA TAQABBAL DU’AAA’E; RABBANAGHFIRLI WALIWALAYDAYYA WA LILMAUMAYNEENA YAUMA YAQUMULHESAB:
SALAM
ASSALAMU ALAIKUM WA RAHMATULLAAH:
OF RIGHTWARDS SALAAM IS TO RIGHTWARDS FARISHTAS AND PRAY OFFERING PEOPLE’S INTENSION BE TAKEN THAT I AM SALAAMING TO THEM AND OF LEFTWARDS SALAAMING TO LEFTWARDS PRAY OFFERING AND FARISHTAS AND WHOM WHAT WARD IS BE THE IMAM SHOULD BE INTENTIONED THAT I AM SALAAMING TO HIM AND LIKEWISE IMAM INTENSION OF BOTH SIDES MUQTADI AND FARISHTAS AND WHEN BE ALONE THEN ONLY OF FARISHTAS.
THIS METHOD OF OFFERING THE PRAY IS FOR MEN. FOR WOMEN IS SOMETHING DIFFERENT. WOMAN WILL LIFT THE HANDS UP TO THE SHOULDERS AT THE TIME OF TAKBEERAY TEHREEMA AND WILL NOT EXIT FROM THE CLOTHES. AT THE TIME OF QIYAM WILL BIND HER HANDS AT THE BREAST AND WILL KEEP PALM AT THE PALM BUT WILL NOT CATCH TO THEM AND FINGERS WILL NOT PUT OPENED. IN THE RUKKU AND SAJOOD WILL DO TIGHTLY. IN THE SAJDAH BELLY WITH THE THIGH AND THIGH WITH THE SPINDLE WILL TOUCH AND HANDS WILL LAY AT THE EARTH. IN THE ATTAHIYAAT FEET TOWARD LEFT OR RIGHT SIDE DOING WILL SIT UPON THE BUTTOCKS AND FINGERS WILL CLOSE; REMAINING ALL IS ACCORDING TO THE MEN IN ISLAM.




“THIS PRAYER IS ACCORDING TO THE MUHAMMAD SHAFFI OF OKARHA SHARIF PAKISTAN FROM A SMALL BOOK FROM NAYAB BOOK CENTER AT REHMAN PURA CHOWK LAHORE, PAKISTAN.”
Thursday, November 30, 2017
